snippet.title: 🎄⛳ Holiday Hideaway Launch Trailer - Walkabout Mini Golf Out Now!
snippet.description:
Tucked away in a log cabin near the North Pole lies a cozy winter hideaway where you can celebrate the holidays with friends and family, or escape from them into quiet solitude! Frolic through the decorations, presents, and charm of this twinkly and nostalgic mini golf now!
